Package com.mimecast.robin.mx

Class MXRoute

java.lang.Object
com.mimecast.robin.mx.MXRoute
public class MXRoute extends Object
MXRoute groups domains that share the same ordered MX server list. It keeps the route hash, the ordered servers and the domains using this route.
